description:
This is a 16 minute workout called ' Precision Power Row' from the channel James Dietz.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor rowing.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Masterclass Workout vibe.
The The Meditative Grind vibe means Zone in, lock down, let repetition take over. This is especially good for Those who love a slow burn and rhythmic intensity. The The Masterclass Workout vibe means Technique-driven, focused, skill-building. This is especially good for Those who love precision and mastery in movement..
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Cultivate the strength to power through anything life throws your way by focusing on every movement with accuracy. Join James for a 15-minute session that hones your strength and precision, equipping you with the skills to face challenges head-on. This workout introduces complex techniques that test your limits while building the resilience needed to overcome adversity. Max rhythm: 30, Format: Intervals...
